 replace your device free of charge.<br/>For further support, you can consult your manual or visit the FLIR website for FAQs. If you prefer to contact FLIR directly about your problems, you can also reach support staff via phone or email."]},"id":"9f97e24c-2be6-4d1d-a249-d98ae2d6a3a9","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"2d7c7706-abc8-40b5-b08e-c82f18410f1e","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Like any camera, the FLIR E60 does have some weaknesses. It lacks autofocus and has only the second-best temperature range, but the E60 does a lot right. It has the best resolution, the most useful features and great extras like an additional battery and charger. The biggest obstacle for most is paying the premium price for a premium product."]},"id":"4bb22640-3fbc-48a8-b476-b3ad6bc01614","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_60712","url":"/flir-e60-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"caleb-cross","url":"/author/caleb-cross","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Caleb Cross","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"MG9CFuiZaQn2UkqAVvekK9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-10-03T22:12:26Z","datePublished":"2014-10-03T22:12:26Z","name":"FLIR E60","synopsis":"The best infrared cameras combine excellent build quality with accurate, high-resolution images and features that make capturing and sharing them easier.","review":{"rating":97,"verdict":"With high resolution and best-in-class features, the E60 is undoubtedly one of the best thermographic cameras available.","pros":["A convenient file format makes sharing easy."],"cons":["This camera lacks autofocus."]},"strapline":"The best infrared cameras combine excellent build quality with accurate, high-resolution images and features that make capturing and sharing them easier.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-10-03T22:12:26Z","id":"2ww6ULy48ob9zLtL7H9kfe","meta":{"title":"FLIR E60 Review - Pros, Cons and Ve